
Soaking




Source: http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Cookbook:Pinto_Beans_Recipe_from_Central_Texas
Name: pinto beans

soak pinto beans with ham bone.

Ingredients

1lb pinto beans
8C water
1t black pepper
1T salt
1 ham bone
1 or 2 bay leaves
5C water
3oz coffee

Instructions
rinse beans with 8oz water
drain and refill with 5 oz.
add othe ingredients
bring to a boil and simmer at least an hour
remove bay leaves
do not drain
served with a slotted spoon
      


